videos.description: On the game's first play from scrimmage, South Carolina QB Ryan Hilinski connects with Shi Smith who takes it 75 yards to the house.

videos.headline: South Carolina scores 75-yard TD on 1st play

videos.description: Tennessee's Marquez Callaway gets his third career punt return touchdown on a 65-yard return to put the Vols up 10-7.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Tennessee returns punt for TD) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Tennessee returns punt for TD

videos.description: QB Jarrett Guarantano finds Jauan Jennings, who sheds multiple defenders en route to a 48-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Jennings goes Beast Mode on Tennessee TD catch) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Jennings goes Beast Mode on Tennessee TD catch

videos.description: South Carolina QB Ryan Hilinski tosses to Bryan Edwards, who rises up and makes a remarkable one-handed grab just shy of the goal line.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (South Carolina's Edwards makes OBJ-like grab) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: South Carolina's Edwards makes OBJ-like grab

videos.description: On fourth-and-goal from the 1-yard line, South Carolina RB Tavien Feaster pounds his way into the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Feaster finds pay dirt on 4th down

videos.description: Tennessee WR Jauan Jennings makes a catch in the back and the end zone and maintains control of the ball despite taking a vicious hit.

videos.headline: Jennings hangs on for Vols TD

videos.description: J.T. Shrout's first career touchdown pass is a memorable one, as he connects with Marquez Callaway in stride for a for 55-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Tennessee airs it out to cushion lead

videos.description: South Carolina's punt is blocked by Daniel Bituli, who recovers the ball in the end zone to give Tennessee a commanding 41-21 lead.
